### List all posts (public)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/posts

### Register user (contoh register manual, jika ada endpoint POST /api/users)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "full_name": "User Satu",
  "avatar_url": "https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=1"
}

### Login (Supabase Auth, biasanya dilakukan di frontend, bukan backend)
# Untuk login Supabase, gunakan SDK di frontend. 
# Jika ingin test login manual, gunakan endpoint Supabase Auth REST API:
POST https://<YOUR_SUPABASE_PROJECT>.supabase.co/auth/v1/token?grant_type=password
apikey: <YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "passwordanda"
}

### Create post (butuh token login, ganti <token> dengan access_token hasil login)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/posts
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Judul Post Baru",
  "slug": "judul-post-baru",
  "content": "Isi artikel",
  "author_id": "uuid-author"
}